      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, it drives smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
