    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and style, perfect for someone seeking a dependable daily driver that has been treated with care. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a car of this age but nothing that detracts from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the dashboard and door panels remain free of cracks or fading. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of all-season tires installed just 3,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two keys, and a thick folder of service records to provide the next owner with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
